---
description: Require translation key constants in frontend code
globs: frontend/src/**/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---

# Translation Key Constants

- Do not pass raw translation key literals directly in frontend TypeScript/TSX.
- Define keys in constant maps under `frontend/src/i18n/keys.ts` (or feature-specific constants modules) and reuse constants.
- Keep constants stable and English-first.
